  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT299-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">ciṟaippuṟamākat tōḻikkuk kiḻatti uraittatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Told by HER to the confidante, while [he] is behind the
          hedge. </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="KT299">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> itumaṟ ṟevaṉō tōḻi mutunīrp</l>
          <l> puṇari tiḷaikkum puḷḷimiḻ kāṉa</l>
          <l> liṇarvīḻ puṉṉai yekkar nīḻaṟ</l>
          <l> puṇarkuṟi vāytta ñāṉṟaik koṇkaṟ</l>
          <l> kaṇṭaṉa maṉṉeṅ kaṇṇē yavaṉcoṟ</l>
          <l> kēṭṭaṉa maṉṉeñ ceviyē maṟṟavaṉ</l>
          <l> maṇappiṉ māṇala meytit</l>
          <l> taṇappiṉ ñekiḻpaveṉ ṟaṭameṉ ṟōḷē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l>Now, what [is] this, friend?</l>
          <l rend="indent">At the time [I] reached the meeting point </l>
          <l rend="indent2">in the shade of the dunes, by the Puṉṉai tree, clusters descending,</l>
          <l rend="indent3">in the seashore grove buzzing with birds, where the waves</l>
          <l rend="indent7">of the old water are jostling,</l>
          <l>our eyes indeed saw the man from the sea,</l>
          <l>our ears indeed heard his words.</l>
          <l rend="indent2">Now if [he] unites with my broad, soft shoulders,</l>
          <l>they reach precious beauty; if he departs, they slacken.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
